TextEng: Farewell.
Should Desther be killed?
Maybe Desther should die?
I go for now.
Why you think he follow Desther?
Why would he follow Desther?
Goodbye.
Will things be getting back to normal now?
Text: 이제 모든 게 정상으로 돌아가게 되겠습니까?

TextEng: I have questions about your fellows.
Text: 동료분들에 대해 몇 가지 물어보고 싶어요.

TextEng: Maybe stuff get normal when this spell get done?
Text: 이 주문 끝나면 다 정상 되는 거야?

TextEng: Me gots questions about other peoples here.
Text: 여기 다른 사람들에 대해 물어볼 거 있어.

TextEng: Me gots questions about the spell thingy.
Text: 그 주문 뭐시기에 대해 물어볼 거 있어.

TextEng: I have questions about the ritual.
Let's go back to my initial questions.
We maybe go back to first questions?
Fenthick says that he gave his ward key to Desther.
Text: 펜딕이 자신의 구역 열쇠를 데스터에게 주었다고 했습니다.

TextEng: Fenthick give his castle key thing to Desther.
Text: 펜딕 자기 성 열쇠 데스터한테 줬대.

TextEng: Desther appears to be a traitor. What are your thoughts?
Desther a traitor. What you think of that?
What do you think of what Fenthick has done?
Text: 펜딕이 한 일에 대해 어떻게 생각하십니까?

TextEng: What you think about what Fenthick do?
Who were the attackers that Desther allowed in?
Who them guys Desther brought to attack us?
Text: 데스터가 들여온 그 공격한 놈들은 누구야?

TextEng: Let's go back to my first questions.
Maybe go back to first questions, okay?
Text: 처음 질문으로 다시 가도 돼, 응?

TextEng: What's Fenthick really done? Nothing outright criminal yet.
Text: 펜딕이 실제로 무엇을 했죠? 아직 명백한 범죄를 저지른 건 아니지 않습니까?

TextEng: Fenthick really that bad? He not do real criminal stuff yet.
Text: 펜딕 정말 그렇게 나빠? 아직 진짜 범죄 저지른 건 없잖아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Investigations in the Docks suggest you knew Vengaul Bloodsail?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 항만 지구 조사에 따르면, 벵골 블러드세일을 아셨던 것 같던데요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Stuff in Docks district say maybe you know Vengaul Bloodsail?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 항만 지구 얘기 보니, 너 벵골 블러드세일 알아?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> New villains, but not the kind you are used to.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 새로운 악당들이라, 원래 상대하시던 유형의 악당들은 아니겠죠.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Does that extend to each other?
